titles.title: A resolution commending the University of Washington women's softball team for winning the 2009 NCAA Women's College World Series.
A resolution commending the University of Washington women's softball team for winning the 2009 NCAA Women's College World Series.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary:
(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Congratulates the University of Washington softball team for winning the 2009 Women's College World Series.
